2004-04-26  Ted Gould  <ted@gould.cx>

	* share/extensions/ai_input.inkmod, share/extensions/dia.inkmod,
	share/extensions/txt2svg.inkmod, src/extension/extension.cpp,
	src/extension/internal/svg.cpp:

